        <p>You've probably tried everything: more coffee, energy drinks, better sleep, vitamins. But here's why none of these address the real problem:</p>

        <p><strong>Coffee gives you a temporary stimulant effect</strong>‚Äîbut it doesn't fix your cellular energy production. It's like revving a car engine that's running out of gas.</p>

